{"tid":1296433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港最大黑社會——香港警賊","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T11:35:25.000Z","uid":208151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aee7ea19b1e68bd05a53a8fb6ba7eee181d0352a","tid":1296433,"uid":208151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"發夢睇住班賊亂狗咁嚟，記者議員女人乜撚都打。<br />\n<br />\n又見到佢地好撚得戚嘅咀臉，又睇住自己交嘅稅款係養緊呢班廢物嘅時候。個心真係好酸，覺得真好唔抵。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你老母啲黑社會仲好撚過佢地</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n交保護費嚟比你地買裝備砌鳩自己？<br />\n<br />\n本身覺得位置唔同佢地無偈，但琴晚夢到嘅係佢地好撚想啲人死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00508fcd60fa77783bc5eef9f64414d59b10dbf","tid":1296433,"uid":262176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf465636227cb03e1c6594c9cdd1c197125e41c","tid":1296433,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"知法犯法, 包庇罪犯, 煽動犯法"}]}